race.description: Akw Accountants & Wealth Advisers Mdn Hcp
race.comment: I'M CHARMING (1) hit the line well on debut over the Riverside and looks ready to go one better with that run under his belt. WILL ONE (3) was nabbed late on debut at Cootamundra, showed early dash again last start but faded. Strips fitter, McDougall sticks, and from the good draw could prove hard to reel in. JUDITH'S REVENGE (7) resumes off a promising first prep and looks to have come on nicely, winning her latest trial here on the Riverside surface. Draws well and looms large. HAZ STYLES (4) backs up quickly from a midfield Albury finish and should relish the rise in trip. Don't underestimate. MADE EASY (2) is a son of Press Statement, debuts for a sharp local stable and arrives off a solid Riverside trial. Respect and watch the market.
